newsitem.title: USA: Iowa-S Minn cattle market not established - USDA.
newsitem.headline: Iowa-S Minn cattle market not established - USDA.

text.p: Slaughter steers and heifers were not established, compared with Friday's close, USDA said. Trade slow. Demand light to moderate with seller interest light. Offerings light.
Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 no sls.
Heifers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 no sls.
